# Test-specific overrides on top of the project's root .clang-tidy.
---
InheritParentConfig: true
Checks: >
  -readability-convert-member-functions-to-static
# readability-convert-member-functions-to-static — Qt Test cases are declared
#   as `private slots:` and must remain non-static member functions so the
#   meta-object system can invoke them; the check mis-flags them.
